{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the same night, the, the whole power was taken over by the extreme elements-- by Hungarian extreme elements, who were called-- not, not-- who have even a sign very similar to, to the swastika, right?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is it the Arrow Cross?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arrow Cross, yes--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know that, the Arrow Cross, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when-- really, that was really the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, you must know that the Russians-- by the-- by August, Romania have defected.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Balkans was, was virtually lost.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when the, the labor camp boys from Bor have been exterminated, pushing up from Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The, the, the, the Eastern Front in Ukraine were very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In, in, in August-- in October, they have been already in Hungary, I would say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would have came through the straits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were in Hungary by that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But, of course, we didn't know that in Budapest exactly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's when these lunatics, lunatics took over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's when the, the hell really broke loose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now we are entering into a period where, where intelligence, money, connections meant absolutely nothing, when luck and your ability to look into somebody's eye, to, to say a word with the right intonation is what counted.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have decided-- I had a very difficult few days, because I knew that I am not going to go back to the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They have been deported in a few days' time, as I learned later on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was-- I was rather-- I was rather helpless for a while.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm-- I wasn't sure what I was going to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I knew that this feeling of, of survival, you know, was getting stronger and stronger in me.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
